### Hadith 3:820

*Narrated Abdullah:*

The Prophet said, "The people of my generation are the best, then those
who follow them, and then whose who follow the latter. After that there
will come some people whose witness will go ahead of their oaths, and
their oaths will go ahead of their witness." Ibrahim (a sub-narrator)
said, "We used to be beaten for taking oaths by saying, 'I bear witness
by the Name of Allah or by the Covenant of Allah."

